subject: libXpm should not try to build into a pure wayland platform.
commitMessage:
libXpm should not try to build into a pure wayland platform.

Tizen devel  | Tizen release
_____________|______________
succeeded    | succeeded
excluded     | excluded
broken       |
failed       |
unresolvable |
blocked      |
locked       |
note:
    - The disabled status is only
      allowed for OBS administration.

Signed-off-by: Ronan Le Martret <ronan@fridu.net>
